en: Amendment No 1 to Project Agreement between the Monitoring of EU Funds Directorate of the Council of Ministers of the Republic of Bulgaria as the National Coordination Unit (NCU) and the Sofia Municipality as well as Sofia Public Electrical Transport Company JSC as the executing Agencies and the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) on the Grant for the Project "Modernized Trams for the City of Sofia" to be implemented during the period 15 October 2015-31 December 2018 in Accordance with the Framework Agreement between the Swiss Federal Council and the Government of the Republic of Bulgaria concerning the Implementation of the Swiss-Bulgarian Cooperation Programme to reduce Economic and Social Disparities within the enlarged European Union, signed on 7 September 2010  - 19-12-2018 - Project Agreement between the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and Monitoring of EU Funds Directorate of the Council of Ministers of the Republic of Bulgaria as the National Coordination Unit (NCU) and the Sofia Municipality as well as Sofia Public Electrical Transport Company JSC as the executing Agencies on the Grant for the Project "Modernized Trams for the City of Sofia" to be implemented during the period 15 October 2015-31 December 2018 in Accordance with the Framework Agreement between the Swiss Federal Council and the Government of the Republic of Bulgaria concerning the Implementation of the Swiss-Bulgarian Cooperation Programme to reduce Economic and Social Disparities within the enlarged European Union, signed on 7 September 2010
